<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١٠٦- أَلَمْ نَخْلُقْكُمْ مِنْ ماءٍ مَهِينٍ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَجَعَلْناهُ فِي قَرارٍ مَكِينٍ <span class="c2">(٢١)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِلى قَدَرٍ مَعْلُومٍ <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَقَدَرْنا فَنِعْمَ الْقادِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٢٣)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِلْمُكَذِّبِينَ <span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١٠٧- أَلَمْ نَجْعَلِ الْأَرْضَ كِفاتاً <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> أَحْياءً وَأَمْواتاً <span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> وَجَعَلْنا فِيها رَواسِيَ شامِخاتٍ وَأَسْقَيْناكُمْ ماءً فُراتاً <span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِلْمُكَذِّبِينَ <span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> انْطَلِقُوا إِلى ما كُنْتُمْ بِهِ تُكَذِّبُونَ <span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>١٠٨- انْطَلِقُوا إِلى ظِلٍّ ذِي ثَلاثِ شُعَبٍ <span class="c2">(٣٠)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لا ظَلِيلٍ وَلا يُغْنِي مِنَ اللَّهَبِ <span class="c2">(٣١)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>إِنَّها تَرْمِي بِشَرَرٍ كَالْقَصْرِ <span class="c2">(٣٢)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>كَأَنَّهُ جِمالَتٌ صُفْرٌ <span class="c2">(٣٣)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِلْمُكَذِّبِينَ <span class="c2">(٣٤)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>هذا يَوْمُ لا يَنْطِقُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَلا يُؤْذَنُ لَهُمْ فَيَعْتَذِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
