<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>وَإِذا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ارْكَعُوا لا يَرْكَعُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٨)</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
